[Quick instruction to install wiliki]

  See the following URL for detailed instruction in Japanese:
  http://www.shiro.dreamhost.com/scheme/wiliki/wiliki.cgi?WiLiKi%3a%a5%ea%a5%d5%a5%a1%a5%ec%a5%f3%a5%b9%a5%de%a5%cb%a5%e5%a5%a2%a5%eb&l=jp


Requirements
------------

  Gauche 0.6.7.1 or later


Installation
------------

The standard configure+make installs necessary modules.

  % ./configure
  % make
  % make install

Then you need to copy src/wiliki.cgi to your cgi script
diretory, and edit the settings.


